These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, asparagus, corn, plum
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, photography, skydiving, chess
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, swimming, rowing, baseball
 1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating plum is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
 4. the person who's sport is sailing is not the person eating plum##6
 5. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
 6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the left of the person eating asparagus##8
 8. the person eating asparagus is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
 9. the person eating grapes is not the person who's hobby is chess##6
10. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's hobby is chess##1
11. the person eating asparagus is not to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##8
12. the person eating asparagus is in an even position##4
13. the person eating plum is not to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##8
14. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food    | grapes         | plum     | corn     | asparagus         |
| Hobby   | photography | chess    | skydiving     | puzzles |
| Sport   | sailing       | swimming | baseball | rowing       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, lemonade, hot-chocolate
The people have 4 different jobs:  videographer, writer, mechanic, lawyer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, cricket, surfing, snowboarding
 1. the mechanic is not to the right of the lawyer##8
 2. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the writer##1
 5. the videographer is not the person drinking lemonade##6
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the videographer##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5
10. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | lemonade          | 7up      | hot-chocolate      | sprite   |
| Job        | mechanic     | videographer | writer | lawyer      |
| Sport      | snowboarding | cricket    | parkour  | surfing |

