.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, traveling, video-games, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, soul, salsa, rock
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, subway, bike, quad-bike
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 2. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
 3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 4. the fan of soul is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
 5. the person driving the skateboard is not the fan of reggae##6
 6. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the fan of reggae is not to the right of the fan of rock##8
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 9. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | video-games  | traveling | skydiving | dancing |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | reggae      | rock | salsa        |
| Transport     | skateboard | bike       | quad-bike    | subway     |

