.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, action, epic, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, disco, electronic, blues
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, indonesian, dutch, nigerian
 1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 2. the indonesian is not to the left of the fan of disco##8
 3. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the person watching animation movies##5
 4. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the indonesian##8
 6. the dutch is not to the right of the person watching satire movies##8
 7. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
 8. the nigerian is somewhere to the right of the indonesian##5
 9. the italian is on the left of the dutch##1
10. the person watching satire movies is the dutch##1
11. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the right of the fan of disco##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation   | satire | action    | epic |
| Music-Genre   | electronic    | disco     | gospel   | blues     |
| Nationality   | italian | dutch   | indonesian | nigerian    |

