The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, adventure, mystery, comedy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, parkour, volleyball, cricket
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##5
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is not the person who's hobby is photography##6
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6
 8. the person watching adventure movies is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 9. the person watching mystery movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
10. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who's hobby is photography##1
11. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the left of the person watching mystery movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | photography       | dancing | video-games  | woodworking    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery       | comedy    | adventure | drama    |
| Sport         | cricket | ice-hockey   | volleyball   | parkour |

