.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, peach, spinach, strawberry
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, superhero, sports, musical
There are 4 different nationalities: british, mexican, polish, indonesian
 1. the person eating spinach is not to the left of the person watching comedy movies##8
 2. the person watching musical movies is not the mexican##6
 3. the polish is somewhere between the person eating peach and the person watching musical movies##7
 4. the mexican is not to the left of the person watching superhero movies##8
 5. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
 6. the polish is the person watching comedy movies##1
 7. the person eating mango is somewhere to the right of the person watching sports movies##5
 8. the indonesian is between the person eating mango and the polish##2
 9. the person watching musical movies is not to the right of the person eating mango##8
10. the person eating spinach is not to the right of the person eating strawberry##8
11. the british is somewhere to the left of the person watching musical movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food          | peach      | spinach      | strawberry | mango |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | comedy    | musical | superhero     |
| Nationality   | british    | polish | indonesian  | mexican |

