 2. the canadian is not the person watching fantasy movies##6
 3. the canadian is between the spanish and the person driving the snowmobile##2
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the spanish##3
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is not the argentine##6
 8. the person watching thriller movies is not to the right of the argentine##8
 9. the argentine is not to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##8
10. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
11. the person watching thriller movies is not to the left of the argentine##8
12. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
13. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5

.:: Answer ::.
