.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, lemonade, juice
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, cherry, plum, mango
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, techno, funk, blues
1. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5
2. the person eating watermelon is somewhere between the person eating mango and the person eating plum##7
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
4. the fan of funk is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
5. the person eating mango is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
6. the person eating watermelon is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
7. the person eating mango is the fan of techno##1
8. the person eating mango is somewhere between the fan of blues and the person drinking tea##7
9. the person eating mango is on the left of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | tea     | hot-chocolate | lemonade  | juice |
| Food          | cherry | mango   | watermelon | plum |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop     | techno   | blues      | funk      |

