.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, writing, collecting, baking
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, french, american
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, quad-bike, roller, bus
 1. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the right of the person driving the tram##8
 2. the american is somewhere between the person driving the bus and the french##7
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the dutch is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
 7. the american is on the left or right of the dutch##3
 8. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 9. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
10. the person driving the roller is not to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##8
11. the dutch is not to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##8
12. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
13. the dutch is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##5
14. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping    | collecting | baking | writing    |
| Nationality   | french  | american    | dutch      | egyptian |
| Transport     | quad-bike | tram          | bus      | roller       |

