 3. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
 4. the person eating nectarine is not to the left of the person eating papaya##8
 5. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
 9. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
10. the person eating spinach is not to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
