 4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the australian##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the analyst##1
 6. the designer is on the right of the electrician##1
 7. the firefighter is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is not the analyst##6
 9. the firefighter is not to the left of the turkish##8
10. the turkish is not to the right of the analyst##8
11. the designer is somewhere between the turkish and the person driving the snowmobile##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |    3     |    4    |
| Job           | electrician  | designer | analyst | firefighter |
| Nationality   | brazilian | australian           | turkish  | egyptian |
| Transport     | snowmobile      | car           | ship     | jet-ski  |

