4. the british is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
5. the argentine is not the person who's sport is cricket##6
6. the owner of the horse is on the left of the italian##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is basketball##7
8. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
9. the person who's sport is cricket is the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | argentine | british     | italian  | german |
| Pet           | frog      | horse        | dog   | lizard |
| Sport         | basketball  | cricket | badminton | rugby       |

 